pullRequest.title: [LW] Rename IdentifiedVersion
pullRequest.bodyText:
Goals (and why):
Rename IdentifiedVersion to something more descriptive
Implementation Description (bullets):
Straightforward
Testing (What was existing testing like?  What have you done to improve it?):
Existing tests pass
Concerns (what feedback would you like?):
I have checked that this object is never serialised outside of our tests, but would appreciate a sanity check as this is definitely not worth a wire format break. In particular, StartTransactionRequestV5 is not serialised anywhere and will be removed in #5005
Where should we start reviewing?:
It's small
Priority (whenever / two weeks / yesterday):
Let's get his in today pls
